faqs.question: What services does Gentle Space Company offer?
faqs.answer: We specialize in leasing, renting, and managing premium office spaces and commercial properties across Bangalore.

faqs.question: Do you only operate in Bangalore?
faqs.answer: Yes, we currently focus exclusively on commercial real estate within Bangalore's prime business districts.

faqs.question: What types of office spaces do you provide?
faqs.answer: We offer a variety of office spaces including co-working spaces, plug-and-play offices, bare shell units, and customized corporate offices.

faqs.question: What is the minimum lease term for an office space?
faqs.answer: The typical minimum lease term is 11 months, but we also offer flexible plans for shorter durations depending on the property.

faqs.question: What types of commercial properties are available?
faqs.answer: We provide retail spaces, showrooms, warehouse spaces, tech parks, and standalone commercial buildings.

faqs.question: Do you offer properties for purchase or only for rent/lease?
faqs.answer: We primarily deal in leasing, but we also have select commercial properties available for sale.

faqs.question: Can I schedule a visit to view a commercial space?
faqs.answer: Absolutely. You can schedule a property tour with our team by filling out the form on our website or calling us directly.

faqs.question: How is the rent or lease price determined?
faqs.answer: Rental pricing depends on the location, size, type of space, and amenities offered. Our team will provide a detailed quote based on your requirements.

faqs.question: Are there any hidden charges?
faqs.answer: No hidden fees. We maintain transparency with all terms including maintenance charges, security deposits, and taxes.

faqs.question: What documents are required to lease a space?
faqs.answer: Common documents include company registration, PAN, ID proof of authorized signatory, and GST certificate (if applicable).

faqs.question: Is there a security deposit required?
faqs.answer: Yes, a standard security deposit (usually 3–10 months' rent) is required depending on the property and lease terms.

faqs.question: Do you offer co-working spaces?
faqs.answer: Yes, we have co-working options in key locations across Bangalore ideal for startups, freelancers, and small teams.

faqs.question: Do you assist in finding office spaces for startups or small businesses?
faqs.answer: Absolutely. We work with businesses of all sizes and offer flexible spaces tailored to your needs and budget.

faqs.question: How do I get started with Gentle Space Company?
faqs.answer: Simply contact us through our website or give us a call, and our team will assist you in finding the right space.
